<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-title">特色蛋品行</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">专注鹌鹑蛋 · 鸽蛋 · 鸭蛋 · 鹅蛋</p>
      <p class="hero-desc">自有养殖基地 · 每日新鲜出品 · 品质保证 · 批发零售</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/products" class="btn btn-primary">查看产品</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline">联系我们</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-seal">
      <div class="seal-ring">
        <div class="seal-text">品质保证</div>
        <div class="seal-inner">鲜</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="features section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">为什么选择我们</h2>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#x1f413;</div>
        <h3>自有养殖基地</h3>
        <p>多年养殖经验，自有鹌鹑、鸽子、鸭、鹅等养殖基地，源头直供，品质可控</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#x1f4e6;</div>
        <h3>每日新鲜配送</h3>
        <p>当天采收、当天发货，全程冷链配送，保证每一枚蛋的新鲜度</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#x2705;</div>
        <h3>品质严格把关</h3>
        <p>每批次抽检，规格分选，确保颗粒均匀、外壳洁净、品质上乘</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#x1f4bc;</div>
        <h3>批零兼营</h3>
        <p>餐饮、食堂、商超批量供应，也支持零售体验，灵活合作</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="categories section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">产品品类</h2>
    <div class="categories-grid">
      <% categories.forEach(function(cat) { %>
      <a href="/products?category=<%= cat.slug %>" class="category-card">
        <div class="category-badge"><%= cat.name %></div>
        <h3><%= cat.name %></h3>
        <p><%= cat.description %></p>
        <span class="category-link">查看详情 &#8594;</span>
      </a>
      <% }); %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="featured section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">热销产品</h2>
    <div class="products-grid">
      <% featured.forEach(function(p) { %>
      <div class="product-card">
        <div class="product-image">
          <div class="product-placeholder"><%= p.name.charAt(0) %></div>
        </div>
        <div class="product-info">
          <span class="product-category"><%= p.category_name %></span>
          <h3 class="product-name"><%= p.name %></h3>
          <p class="product-desc"><%= p.description.length > 20 ? p.description.substring(0, 20) + '...' : p.description %></p>
          <div class="product-meta">
            <span class="product-price">&#xffe5;<%= p.price.toFixed(1) %></span>
            <span class="product-unit">/ <%= p.unit %></span>
          </div>
          <a href="/products/<%= p.slug %>" class="btn btn-sm">查看详情</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% }); %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="trust section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="trust-content">
      <h2 class="section-title">诚信经营 · 口碑相传</h2>
      <div class="trust-stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">10+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">年行业经验</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">50+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">合作餐饮企业</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">100+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">长期合作伙伴</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">500+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">日均供应量</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="cta section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>欢迎咨询合作</h2>
    <p>如需大量采购或长期合作，欢迎来电或到访考察</p>
    <p class="cta-phone">联系电话：400-888-8888</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">联系我们</a>
  </div>
</section>
